:rubric=3. Eyes.
S{Very severe orbital neuralgia over r. eye.} S{Pupils dilated.}


:rubric=5. Nose.
S{Tight and stopped up.} S{Tickling, prickling, itching in nostrils.} S{Sense of smell very acute.} S{Ozaena, with great fetor and ulceration.}


