S{Urine: dark greenish brown; greenish; very dark; black or blackish.} S{Quantity increased and passed frequently.} S{Diabetes.} S{Albuminuria.} S{Urine of high specific gravity; urea abundant.} S{While urinating always an involuntary mucous discharge from anus.}


